{"tid":766753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【跪低】支那商務部回應企業被列入管制清單　求美國放寬出口管制","createTime":"2018-08-04T00:57:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-04T01:23:02.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a587c949a0cd197cc0c8ba12b3b2302e48d34095","tid":766753,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T00:57:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1410558_2_L_20180804032730.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1410558_2_L_20180804032730.jpg&h=204e97cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n支那商務部發言人晚上回應美國政府，將部分支那實體及企業列入出口管制清單，指支方反對美方動輒對支方實體實施單邊制裁的立場從未改變，敦促美方採取切實措施，放寬對支那出口管制，保護和促進雙方企業開展高技術貿易與合作，維護雙方企業的合法權益。<br />\n<br />\n美國商務部以國家安全為理由，星期三宣布將44間支那企業列入出口管制實體清單，實施技術封鎖。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n支那快D技術封銷返<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">新四大發明</span></span>報復美國啦！"},{"pid":"67e5abebe225e5c3753d3d239d115800b6037d63","tid":766753,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T01:23:02.000Z","msg":"入肉了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}